  section.section-top-faq#faq
    .wrapper
      h2.sec-heading
        small General Queries
        strong Frequently Asked Questions
      p.sec-description Have questions about our HTML coding service? <br class="md">Check out our detailed FAQ section for expert insights and guidance.
      ul.list-faq
        li
          h3.item-title Do I need to provide a complete design for my website?
          p.item-text No, you don’t need a fully polished design. We’re happy to work with drafts, mockups, or even rough ideas you’ve sketched out. Whatever you have, we’ll turn it into functional HTML code.
        li
          h3.item-title What makes your HTML coding service different?
          p.item-text We offer a unique <a href="/kb/true-liquid-layout.html" target="_blank">True Liquid Layout</a> approach, which we haven’t seen replicated elsewhere—it ensures your website adapts seamlessly to any screen size with exceptional fluidity. Beyond that, we stand out with our clean, optimized code, fast turnaround
        li
          h3.item-title Do you use frameworks or libraries like Bootstrap?
          p.item-text We don’t include libraries like Bootstrap by default because they can make the site heavier and may be unnecessary for your needs. That said, if you request them or they suit your project, we’re happy to integrate them.
        li
          h3.item-title How long does it take to complete a project?
          p.item-text The timeline depends on the project’s scope. A basic webpage might take 1-3 days, while a larger site with multiple pages or custom features could take 1-2 weeks. Once we discuss your needs, we’ll provide a detailed estimate tailored to your project.
        li
          h3.item-title Do you only work with HTML Coding, or can you handle other technologies too?
          p.item-text While our core focus is HTML Coding, we’re skilled in CSS for styling and JavaScript for interactivity. We can also work with frameworks like Vue, React, or collaborate with backend developers to integrate your front-end with systems like PHP or Node.js. Let us know what you need!
        li
          h3.item-title How much do your services cost?
          p.item-text Pricing varies based on complexity and requirements. A simple HTML page might start at $50-$100, while full-site builds or ongoing maintenance could range higher. We offer free consultations to understand your project and provide a custom quote.
        li
          h3.item-title What payment methods do you accept?
          p.item-text We accept all common payment methods. We’ll provide the full list of options when we get in touch to discuss your project.
        li
          h3.item-title Can you help me with design?
          p.item-text Yes, we have skilled designers on our team who can assist you with creating a design that suits your needs.
        li
          h3.item-title Can you update or fix my existing website?
          p.item-text Absolutely! We can troubleshoot errors, improve responsiveness, update outdated code, or enhance functionality. Send us your website details, and we’ll assess what needs to be done.
        li
          h3.item-title Do you provide support after the project is complete?
          p.item-text Yes, we offer post-launch support for any tweaks or issues that arise. Depending on your needs, we can arrange ongoing maintenance or one-time fixes—just let us know what works for you.
        li
          h3.item-title How do I get started with your service?
          p.item-text It’s simple! Contact us through the form on this website, share your project details (like goals, timeline, and budget), and we’ll get back to you within 24 hours to discuss next steps.

